### Get All Contacts
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Single Contact
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts/1
Content-Type: application/json

### Create New Contact
POST http://localhost:3000/contacts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "Johnson",
  "email": "alice.johnson@example.com",
  "favoriteColor": "Purple",
  "birthday": "1992-03-15"
}

### Update Contact
PUT http://localhost:3000/contacts/3
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "Johnson",
  "email": "alice.johnson.updated@example.com",
  "favoriteColor": "Blue",
  "birthday": "1992-03-15"
}

### Delete Contact
DELETE http://localhost:3000/contacts/3
Content-Type: application/json